      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it remains in showroom condition with no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to excellence, offering an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning professional. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
